### Sample API Requests for Python Bad Code API Testing
### Bad practice: storing test data with hardcoded values

### Login as admin (will fail due to bad code!)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/main/Login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@store.com",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### Add Product
POST http://localhost:8000/api/main/AddProduct
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Python Laptop",
  "price": 1199.99,
  "stock": 15,
  "description": "High-performance laptop for Python development"
}

### Get Product
GET http://localhost:8000/api/main/GetProduct?id=1000

### Search Products  
GET http://localhost:8000/api/main/SearchProducts?query=laptop&sortBy=Price&filterBy=expensive

### Add to Cart
POST http://localhost:8000/api/main/AddToCart
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 1000,
  "name": "Gaming Laptop", 
  "price": 1299.99,
  "quantity": 1,
  "category": "electronics"
}

### Get Cart
GET http://localhost:8000/api/main/GetCart

### Create Order
POST http://localhost:8000/api/main/CreateOrder
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "paymentMethod": "credit_card"
}

### Process Payment
POST http://localhost:8000/api/main/ProcessPayment
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "method": "credit_card",
  "amount": 1149.99,
  "cardNumber": "1234567890123456", 
  "cvv": "123",
  "expiry": "12/25"
}

### Update Order Status
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/main/UpdateOrderStatus?orderId=5000&newStatus=shipped

### Get Order
GET http://localhost:8000/api/main/GetOrder?id=5000

### Get Stats (exposes internal state!)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/main/GetStats

### Calculate Utility
POST http://localhost:8000/api/main/Calculate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "subtotal": 100.00,
  "type": "tax"
}

### Logout
POST http://localhost:8000/api/main/Logout